syntaxtree 中 Node 的使用
 

syntaxtree 中 Node 的子接口
 interface NodeListInterface
          The interface which NodeList, NodeListOptional, and NodeSequence implement.
 

实现 Node 的 syntaxtree 中的类
 class AllocationExpression
          Grammar production: f0 -> "new" f1 -> Identifier() f2 -> "(" f3 -> ")"
 class AndExpression
          Grammar production: f0 -> PrimaryExpression() f1 -> "&&" f2 -> PrimaryExpression()
 class ArrayAllocationExpression
          Grammar production: f0 -> "new" f1 -> "int" f2 -> "[" f3 -> Expression() f4 -> "]"
 class ArrayAssignmentStatement
          Grammar production: f0 -> Identifier() f1 -> "[" f2 -> Expression() f3 -> "]" f4 -> "=" f5 -> Expression() f6 -> ";"
 class ArrayLength
          Grammar production: f0 -> PrimaryExpression() f1 -> "."
 class ArrayLookup
          Grammar production: f0 -> PrimaryExpression() f1 -> "[" f2 -> PrimaryExpression() f3 -> "]"
 class ArrayType
          Grammar production: f0 -> "int" f1 -> "[" f2 -> "]"
 class AssignmentStatement
          Grammar production: f0 -> Identifier() f1 -> "=" f2 -> Expression() f3 -> ";"
 class Block
          Grammar production: f0 -> "{" f1 -> ( Statement() )* f2 -> "}"
 class BooleanType
          Grammar production: f0 -> "boolean"
 class BracketExpression
          Grammar production: f0 -> "(" f1 -> Expression() f2 -> ")"
 class ClassDeclaration
          Grammar production: f0 -> "class" f1 -> Identifier() f2 -> "{" f3 -> ( VarDeclaration() )* f4 -> ( MethodDeclaration() )* f5 -> "}"
 class ClassExtendsDeclaration
          Grammar production: f0 -> "class" f1 -> Identifier() f2 -> "extends" f3 -> Identifier() f4 -> "{" f5 -> ( VarDeclaration() )* f6 -> ( MethodDeclaration() )* f7 -> "}"
 class CompareExpression
          Grammar production: f0 -> PrimaryExpression() f1 -> "<" f2 -> PrimaryExpression()
 class Expression
          Grammar production: f0 -> AndExpression() | CompareExpression() | PlusExpression() | MinusExpression() | TimesExpression() | ArrayLookup() | ArrayLength() | MessageSend() | PrimaryExpression()
 class ExpressionList
          Grammar production: f0 -> Expression() f1 -> ( ExpressionRest() )*
 class ExpressionRest
          Grammar production: f0 -> "," f1 -> Expression()
 class FalseLiteral
          Grammar production: f0 -> "false"
 class FormalParameter
          Grammar production: f0 -> Type() f1 -> Identifier()
 class FormalParameterList
          Grammar production: f0 -> FormalParameter() f1 -> ( FormalParameterRest() )*
 class FormalParameterRest
          Grammar production: f0 -> "," f1 -> FormalParameter()
 class Goal
          Grammar production: f0 -> MainClass() f1 -> ( TypeDeclaration() )* f2 ->
 class Identifier
          Grammar production: f0 ->
 class IfStatement
          Grammar production: f0 -> "if" f1 -> "(" f2 -> Expression() f3 -> ")" f4 -> Statement() f5 -> "else" f6 -> Statement()
 class IntegerLiteral
          Grammar production: f0 ->
 class IntegerType
          Grammar production: f0 -> "int"
 class MainClass
          Grammar production: f0 -> "class" f1 -> Identifier() f2 -> "{" f3 -> "public" f4 -> "static" f5 -> "void" f6 -> "main" f7 -> "(" f8 -> "String" f9 -> "[" f10 -> "]" f11 -> Identifier() f12 -> ")" f13 -> "{" f14 -> PrintStatement() f15 -> "}" f16 -> "}"
 class MessageSend
          Grammar production: f0 -> PrimaryExpression() f1 -> "."
 class MethodDeclaration
          Grammar production: f0 -> "public" f1 -> Type() f2 -> Identifier() f3 -> "(" f4 -> ( FormalParameterList() )?
 class MinusExpression
          Grammar production: f0 -> PrimaryExpression() f1 -> "-" f2 -> PrimaryExpression()
 class NodeChoice
          Represents a grammar choice, e.g. ( A | B )
 class NodeList
          Represents a grammar list, e.g. ( A )+
 class NodeListOptional
          Represents an optional grammar list, e.g. ( A )*
 class NodeOptional
          Represents an grammar optional node, e.g. ( A )?
 class NodeSequence
          Represents a sequence of nodes nested within a choice, list, optional list, or optional, e.g. ( A B )+ or [ C D E ]
 class NodeToken
          Represents a single token in the grammar.
 class NotExpression
          Grammar production: f0 -> "!"
 class PlusExpression
          Grammar production: f0 -> PrimaryExpression() f1 -> "+" f2 -> PrimaryExpression()
 class PrimaryExpression
          Grammar production: f0 -> IntegerLiteral() | TrueLiteral() | FalseLiteral() | Identifier() | ThisExpression() | ArrayAllocationExpression() | AllocationExpression() | NotExpression() | BracketExpression()
 class PrintStatement
          Grammar production: f0 -> "System.out.println" f1 -> "(" f2 -> Expression() f3 -> ")" f4 -> ";"
 class Statement
          Grammar production: f0 -> Block() | AssignmentStatement() | ArrayAssignmentStatement() | IfStatement() | WhileStatement() | PrintStatement()
 class ThisExpression
          Grammar production: f0 -> "this"
 class TimesExpression
          Grammar production: f0 -> PrimaryExpression() f1 -> "*" f2 -> PrimaryExpression()
 class TrueLiteral
          Grammar production: f0 -> "true"
 class Type
          Grammar production: f0 -> ArrayType() | BooleanType() | IntegerType() | Identifier()
 class TypeDeclaration
          Grammar production: f0 -> ClassDeclaration() | ClassExtendsDeclaration()
 class VarDeclaration
          Grammar production: f0 -> Type() f1 -> Identifier() f2 -> ";"
 class WhileStatement
          Grammar production: f0 -> "while" f1 -> "(" f2 -> Expression() f3 -> ")" f4 -> Statement()
